學科既學額<br />\n做得大學高層全部都世界仔 你估高層真係唔知咁樣開科on9咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過條大水喉係教資會到 唔跟就cut你budget<br />\non9都要開一個新科<br />\n以後只會更多新科，或者新科比人殺"},{"pid":"c41631c284730a97979f9a819034d80f0bd65dc5","tid":826873,"uid":21456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a00a4227f63da4ef62b4a0666e6122f6a726273","tid":826873,"uid":147629,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T14:32:45.000Z","msg":"好心UGC直接擺多啲資源落高等教育，唔使啲院校開埋開埋越嚟越多職訓programme，真正搞學術嘅programme就要cut。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T14:37:52.000Z","msg":"Applied AI 都可以 research oriented 既<br />\n但佢既program core requirement 完全唔夠囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過都要睇佢之後個structure同開咩新course先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"993e1cbd0e5712024a2ce0b8dd7f6fe2aa1c827e","tid":826873,"uid":21456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T14:38:58.000Z","msg":"搞個cross faculty program又呃到人入U <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb0f661d59b16d62c19f047f9b779af628df8ab5","tid":826873,"uid":126510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1cf858b53424c48e0db09ce6c6cbecb59f904f0f","tid":826873,"uid":147629,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b83f661bbbe518447e8a0e12df3c85ca7553ca72","tid":826873,"uid":126510,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T14:21:25.000Z","msg":"老老實實讀呢d科不如正正經經讀個 computer science<br />\n<br />\n升學人地又唔知你呢科做乜鳩<br />\n搵工又要解釋一大輪"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T14:30:28.000Z","msg":"要讀AI就直情唔會揀HKU啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想知CS Dept又host fintech又搞AI，請夠人未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家有冇五個fulltime prof嘅research interest係fintech or AI related<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" cl